I really am a fan of this artstyle and it definitely deserves the attention it gets. All three of the girl are drawn beautifully and so critically, it's hard to not see the effort that was put into this, especially considering that it's full colour. However, I do wish for this artist to work on some of the other girls someday, however long that may take. Especially since more than half of the pages shown here are the same things we've already seen, it makes this feel somewhat repetitive in a way. No fault of the artist itself, but it's still something to keep in mind. It is still a pretty well made doujin though, and I respect the artist greatly.
